description: Website sitemap data that outlines the structure of web pages, including their update frequency and importance, aiding in search engine optimization and content management.

metadata.description: Frequency at which the content of the URL is expected to change; Indicates how often the page is updated.
The URL location of the resource; Represents the web address of the sitemap entry.
Indicates the importance of the URL in the sitemap; A higher value signifies a higher priority for search engines.
